{%- comment -%}
  JSON-LD Review Schema (Schema.org)
  Renders aggregateRating + individual reviews from metafields.
  Include on product pages: {% render 'schema-review', product: product %}

  Expected metafields:
    product.metafields.reviews.rating       → { rating: "4.5", scale_min: "1", scale_max: "5" }
    product.metafields.reviews.rating_count  → number
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- comment -%}
  Note: Review schema is embedded within schema-product.liquid as aggregateRating.
  This snippet handles standalone review display if additional review data
  is available via metafields (e.g., from a reviews app).

  Individual reviews can be added here when the shop uses a reviews app
  that stores review data in metafields.
{%- endcomment -%}

{%- if product.metafields.reviews.rating.value != blank -%}
  {%- comment -%}
    aggregateRating is already included in schema-product.liquid.
    This snippet is a placeholder for individual Review objects
    when review content metafields become available.
  {%- endcomment -%}
{%- endif -%}
